<h3 align=center>ORDERING INFORMATION</h3><p>
</center><p>
<p>
	Unless otherwise indicated, a single reprint or photocopy of a listed
publication, report, or abstract is available free of charge from the
sole/senior NEFSC author of the work (i.e., as depicted by all capital
letters).  The correct mailing address for the sole/senior Center author is
indicated by a two-letter code at the end of the bibliographic entry.  The key
to the codes is as follows:<p>
<p>
<p>
MF =	National Marine Fisheries Service, 212 Rogers Ave., Milford, CT 06460<p>
