<p>         NE3       44 04.4' N.         67 48.7' W.
<p>         NE4       44 06.9' N.         67 52.8' W.
<p>         NE5       44 31.2' N.         67 02.7' W.
<p>         NE6       Maine shoreline     67 02.7' W.
<p>                                                       
