W.
34. Scotland Horn Buoy "S", off Sandy Hook (NJ)   40 26.5' N.         73 55.0'
W.
35. Barnegat Lighted Gong Buoy "2"      39 45.5' N.         73 59.5' W.
36. A point east of Atlantic City Light      39 21.9' N.         74 22.7' W.
37. A point east of Hereford Inlet Light          39 00.4' N.         74 46'
W.
