<DOCNO>WT12-B25-24</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000578-B036-134</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://monk.wh.whoi.edu:80/library/sos94/flt/flt.html 128.128.104.203 19970103031624 text/html 4748
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 03:16:30 GMT
