<font COLOR="#555555" size=+1>
<p> <a name="q11"><b><h3>What fishes are named after other animals?<p> 
</b></h3></a>

<font COLOR="#888888" size=+1>
<blockquote>
Many are named after animals including - alligator, bird, boar, buffalo,
cat, cow, <a
href="http://www.wh.whoi.edu/library/sos94/spsyn/op/dogfish.html">dog</a>, elephant, frog, goat, goose, hawk, horse,  eagle,
leopard, lizard, parrot, porcupine, rabbit, sheep, pig, squirrel, hog,
tiger, toad, unicorn, viper, wolf, scorpion, zebra, robin, raven. 
<a href="http://www.skio.peachnet.edu/noaa/fishguide.html">See the Illustrated Field
Guide to Fishes of Gray's Reef</a> and <a
href="http://kingfish.ssp.nmfs.gov/fish.html"> NOAA Fisheries Headquarters</a> for more illustrations<br>

</font>
</blockquote>
