<DOCNO>WT12-B25-132</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000578-B034-2</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://monk.wh.whoi.edu:80/library/sos94/spsyn/og/cusk.html 128.128.104.203 19970103030526 text/html 3940
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
